ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; LOOTING; WOMEN; EVACUATIONS; GUERRILLAS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ 
-- FOREIGN POPULATIONS; GANGS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- ANNEXATIONS 
</P>
