EMBARGOES; DEFENSE SPENDING; MIDDLE EAST -- FOREIGN AID; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- JAPAN; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SOUTH KOREA 
</P>
