PROGRAMS -- UNITED STATES; SPACE SHUTTLE; DISCOVERY (SPACE SHUTTLE); SCHEDULES; 
DIAGNOSTIC TESTS; NATIONAL AERONAUTICS AND SPACE ADMINISTRATION 
</P>
