<P>
Xerox Replacement Guarantee: The "Total Satisfaction Guarantee" promises a free 
replacement to customers dissatisfied with any of the company's products 
delivered from now on for three years, or for the full term of financing 
through Rochester, N.Y.-based Xerox, whichever is longer. 
</P>
