<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN GABRIEL TO PAY COUNTY TO FIX STREETS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The San Gabriel City Council voted unanimously Tuesday to pay Los Angeles 
County about $32,000 to repair cracked streets in the northeast part of the 
city. 
</P>
<P>
No date been set for the project to start. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
