ENTERTAINMENT INDUSTRY -- LOS ANGELES; MOTION PICTURE INDUSTRY -- LOS ANGELES; 
TELEVISION INDUSTRY -- LOS ANGELES; GROWTH MANAGEMENT 
</P>
