identified Daveyon James, whose arm was broken in a car accident in South Los 
Angeles. The story accompanying the photo also should have stated that an 
injured playmate, David Jennings, was being treated for a broken thigh at 
Martin Luther King, Jr./Drew Medical Center. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
