<P>
Photo, COLOR, SUNSET LEAGUE: Ocean View has built its offense around 
quarterback Randy Karliner. Tenth in a series. PETER ROSS / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Ocean View's offense is built around senior quarterback Randy Karliner, 
a three-year starter. PETER ROSS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
